      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that\u2019s ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear consistent with its age, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone looking for reliable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s been well-loved and is perfect for a driver who prioritizes utility and character over a showroom finish!",
